 card and told me to e-mail him when I book and before I arrive and they will the same room available for me next time. Couldn't help but feel impressed. As for the previous reviews, the closest casino was the Wynn or Treasure Island if you cut through the mall was about a 15 minute walk away from entrance to entrance which wasn't to bad. For food our room came with a fully decked kitchen, and ABC was in the mall to pick up extras if wanted. Didn't actually eat the Trump but the mall had a wide array of food choices but you must try Maggiano’s in the mall simply excellent Italian food and the most reasonable. By the way rooms were very clean and never did find a baggie of Cocaine in my room... ;) Sorry just had to.	
