ll which was the dearest and Denys they were exellent and you were seated quickly.We all had a fantastic stay, one week was not long enough for us, we never stopped but did not see everything.We caught a Taxi back to the airport, the driver was really friendly, the Taxi bill was $15 we were so pleased we gave him $20.When you read up before you go you get the impression you have to constantly give Tips, this is not true, we gave tips when we thought they had been earned.We cannot wait to go to Vegas again.	
